snippet.title: Island Keeper Demo Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Gameplay Trailer of the 3D Adventure-Simulator "Island Keeper" about world pollution and ecology
Wishlist it on Steam!

Demo version will be available on 11 October 2024!
